#Text=DS : That seems cliché .
#Text=Veronica : Yeah , it ’s cliché .
#Text=DS :
#Text=If people come in with post-traumatic stress disorder , are there special considerations ?
#Text=Veronica : Yeah .
#Text=Jada : Yes , I think we ’ve dealt with a lot of people who have those issues .
#Text=Veronica : I ca n’t say I have had anyone who wanted to re-enact an Abu Ghraib experience , though .
#Text=Boundaries
#Text=DS : Are there places you just wo n’t go ?
#Text=Veronica : Psychological ?
#Text=No.
#Text=DS : What about physically ?
#Text=Veronica : Yes , I have my boundaries , but I prefer not to define them .
#Text=Jada :
#Text=I think everyone does .
#Text=It would always depend , it would be difficult to state what would be my boundary .
#Text=One minute it can be one thing , and another client might come in and say , “ Can you do this , this and that , ” and the answer is no .
#Text=[ Laughs ]
#Text=DS :
#Text=Have you ever had a session where you felt threatened ?
#Text=Veronica : No. I feel quite safe here , because they know we outnumber them .

#Text=Okay , in terms of boundaries , if I ’m a sub and the man is a dom , I do n’t let him blindfold me AND put a gag in my mouth , because then there is no way to tell what he is going to do and alert anyone .
#Text=There are certain safe words that you use , and if people do n’t respect those boundaries then you remind them of the boundaries or else you can end the session .
#Text=DS : Have you had to end a session ?
#Text=Veronica : Yes .
#Text=DS : Can you tell me about a time ?
#Text=Veronica : One time somebody was really forceful about wanting to see my panties .
#Text=It was a trampling session , where you step on his face .
#Text=He wanted me to step on his face , but he did n't want me to step on his face , he wanted to look up my skirt .
#Text=So I ended the session and I told him I knew that he was doing that , because every time I tried to step on his face he would move it and try to look up my skirt .
#Text=So I ended it .
#Text=He was an asshole .
#Text=DS : Will you do full nudity ?
#Text=Veronica : No.
#Text=Jada : No.
#Text=DS : Topless ?
#Text=Veronica : Yeah , it ’s pretty common that we are topless .
#Text=DS : Is full nudity uncommon ?
#Text=Veronica : No , I do n’t think so .
#Text=DS : Why do you prefer not to do it ?
#Text=Veronica : I just do n’t feel comfortable , and if I do n’t feel comfortable I just do n’t do it .
#Text=And I think a lot of people will do that because they want to please the customer and have them come back , but ultimately I do n’t think that is good for you psychologically .
#Text=Jada : Yes , if you are not 100 % with everything you do , then it ’s going to affect you .
